2002-0238 (La. 10/25/02)

STATE of Louisiana v. Dwayne SIMMONS. No. 2002-K-0238. Supreme Court of Louisiana. Oct. 25, 2002.

In re Simmons, Dwayne; — Defendant; Applying for Supervisory and/or Remedial Writs, Parish of Lafourche, 17th Judicial District Court Div. C, No. 333145; to the Court of Appeal, First Circuit, No. 2001 KA 0169.

Denied.

JOHNSON, J., would grant the writ.
